menuconfig ZMK_LED_STATUS
    bool "LED-based keyboard status indicators"
    depends on ZMK_RGB_UNDERGLOW
    depends on SHIELD_EYELASH_CORNE_LEFT
    default y
    help
      Enable the LED status system for the Eyelash Corne left (central) half.
      Uses per-key RGB LEDs to indicate Bluetooth profile, pairing state,
      host connection, split connection, and battery level.
      LEDs are off by default and only illuminate during brief event-driven
      animations, keeping power consumption minimal.
